# Keep the Docker build context small (context = repo root for the rag-engine image).
.git
.github
.gitignore
.idea
**/*.iml
.vscode
**/node_modules
**/.venv
**/__pycache__
**/.pytest_cache
**/.ruff_cache
docs
*.md
**/README.md
infra
# …but the UI image (ui/Dockerfile) needs the proxy Caddyfile baked in (re-include it).
!infra/proxy
!infra/proxy/Caddyfile
# …and the Java images (gateway/rag-engine/mcp-tools) compile the health probe from this file.
!infra/docker
!infra/docker/HealthCheck.java
# Java build noise we don't need in the image (we only copy the fat jar explicitly):
**/target/classes
**/target/generated-sources
**/target/maven-status
**/target/surefire-reports
**/target/test-classes
